    <item>
      <title>印度议会通过有争议的穆斯林财产法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/india-parliament-passes-controversial-muslim-property-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度议会通过了一项有争议的数十年的法律，该法律涉及了一项有争议的数十年法律，该法律是为了宗教和慈善目的而捐赠的穆斯林拥有的财产，这两家房屋都在漫长的辩论之后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/india-parliament-passes-controversial-muslim-property-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 04:22:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曼谷清除了倒塌的塔的碎片，数十个仍缺失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bangkok-clears-debris-of-collapsed-tower-as-dozens-still-missing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[曼谷市政府开始清理上周地震坠毁的塔楼的碎屑，因为在数十名工人中发现幸存者的希望仍然被困在几乎已经结束了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bangkok-clears-debris-of-collapsed-tower-as-dozens-still-missing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 04:19:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布加勒斯特市市长出价，担任Tiktok领导的竞选活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bucharest-mayor-bids-for-presidency-with-tiktok-led-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布加勒斯特市市长尼古斯·丹（Nicusor Dan）注意到观众中的每个人都停止听他的声音，因此获得了公民奖。他们都是疯狂地在手机上滚动的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bucharest-mayor-bids-for-presidency-with-tiktok-led-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
